Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_bell_lookup#

The QOS/GRP table contains 16 entries with 16 QOS/GRP pairs per entry 256 pairs total. HW selects the FIFO by using the fields determined by the SRIO_BELL_SELECT register to parse the doorbell packet. The actual FIFO number selected is limited by the SRIO()_RX_BELL_CTRL[NUM_FIFO]. For example, if NUM_FIFO has a value of 011 (4 FIFOs) then only the two LSBs of the FIFO number stored in the SRIO_BELL_LOOKUP are used.

This register is reset by the h-clock reset.
